    """Resolve mapping-based dynamic defaults on :class:`Option`
    parameters now that command line arguments, environment
    variables, and configuration files have all been processed.

    A dynamic default only replaces a value whose source is still
    :attr:`ParameterSource.DEFAULT`, so any value explicitly
    provided elsewhere is left untouched.
